        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 110. Phylogenetic tree of specimens of the species related to Anolis liogaster from a maximum-likelihood analysis of DNA sequences of two mitochondrial genes: (a) 16S rRNA and (b) CO1. A scale bar is indicated. The numbers at nodes are bootstrap values. The tree is rooted with the species Anolis stevepoei." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4931183/files/figure.png" .

